<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Steven_Milloy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: News coverage">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">News coverage</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="http://www.prwatch.org/prwissues/1999Q4/avery.html" class="external text" title="http://www.prwatch.org/prwissues/1999Q4/avery.html" rel="nofollow">Saving the Planet With Pestilent Statistics</a>,</i> article by Karen Charman, <i><a href="/wiki/PR_Watch" title="PR Watch">PR Watch</a>,</i> Fourth Quarter 1999, Volume 6, No. 4</li>
<li><i><a href="http://www.prwatch.org/prwissues/2000Q3/junkman.html" class="external text" title="http://www.prwatch.org/prwissues/2000Q3/junkman.html" rel="nofollow">How Big Tobacco Helped Create "the Junkman"</a>,</i> article by <a href="/wiki/Sheldon_Rampton" title="Sheldon Rampton">Sheldon Rampton</a> and <a href="/wiki/John_Stauber" title="John Stauber">John Stauber</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/PR_Watch" title="PR Watch">PR Watch</a>,</i> Third Quarter 2000, Volume 7, No. 3</li>
<li><i><a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20070927190615/http://www.freepress.net/news/print.php?id=13581" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20070927190615/http://www.freepress.net/news/print.php?id=13581" rel="nofollow">At Fox News, a Pundit for Hire</a>,</i> article by <a href="/wiki/Paul_D._Thacker" title="Paul D. Thacker">Paul D. Thacker</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/The_New_Republic" title="The New Republic">The New Republic</a>,</i> <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2006-01-27"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="01-27"><a href="/wiki/January_27" title="January 27">January 27</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2006" title="2006">2006</a></span> (<a href="/wiki/Internet_Archive" title="Internet Archive">Internet Archive</a>)</li>
<li><i><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2006/sep/19/ethicalliving.g2" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2006/sep/19/ethicalliving.g2" rel="nofollow">The Denial Industry</a>,</i> article by <a href="/wiki/George_Monbiot" title="George Monbiot">George Monbiot</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/The_Guardian" title="The Guardian">The Guardian</a></i>, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2006-09-19"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="09-19"><a href="/wiki/September_19" title="September 19">September 19</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2006" title="2006">2006</a></span></li>
<li><i><a href="http://www.motherjones.com/news/feature/2005/05/some_like_it_hot.html" class="external text" title="http://www.motherjones.com/news/feature/2005/05/some_like_it_hot.html" rel="nofollow">Some Like It Hot</a>,</i> article by <a href="/wiki/Chris_Mooney" title="Chris Mooney">Chris Mooney</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/Mother_Jones_(magazine)" title="Mother Jones (magazine)">Mother Jones</a>,</i> May/June 2005</li>
<li><i><a href="http://www.skeptictank.org/hs/tscience.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.skeptictank.org/hs/tscience.htm" rel="nofollow">If You Seek the Truth, Don't Trash the Science</a>,</i> article by John Schwartz, <i><a href="/wiki/Washington_Post" title="Washington Post" class="mw-redirect">Washington Post</a>,</i> <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1999-02-21"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="02-21"><a href="/wiki/February_21" title="February 21">February 21</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1999" title="1999">1999</a></span></li>
<li><i><a href="http://www.exxonsecrets.org/html/personfactsheet.php?id=881" class="external text" title="http://www.exxonsecrets.org/html/personfactsheet.php?id=881" rel="nofollow">Factsheet: Steven Milloy</a></i> at <i>Exxonsecrets</i> (<a href="/wiki/Greenpeace" title="Greenpeace">Greenpeace</a>)</li>
</ul>


